Exchange order book right now.

00:33:12.540 --> 00:33:15.020
Whether you can in 10
years, I'm not sure.

00:33:15.020 --> 00:33:19.740
But time latency is so relevant
in the middle of those order

00:33:19.740 --> 00:33:20.830
books--

00:33:20.830 --> 00:33:22.860
you know, the
